:information_source:  *Unit Test Coverage Reports* :information_source: 

Releng has added coverage.cicd.instabase.com (http://coverage.cicd.instabase.com) for viewing unit test coverage of the instabase repo :tada:

This is still a WIP and therefore does not contain coverage reports for *all* code, but it does currently
• Collect lcov-based reports for golang code that is currently built with Bazel
• Publish updated reports every 12 hours
We are working on incorporating reports for code not built with Bazel, however you can easily add your code before releng has time to do it for you by onboarding to Bazel!

If you have any questions or concerns please reach out in <#C035SLYCJ9X|> :slightly_smiling_face:

cc @shaunak @Aaron Tami <!subteam^S038TM462UX>
